210
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:45,120
我不明白
I don't understand.

211
00:08:46,050 --> 00:08:47,600
我是加来战役的英雄  葛瑞尔
I'm a hero of Calais, Greer.

212
00:08:47,650 --> 00:08:49,160
我救了王子的命
I saved the Dauphin's life.

213
