I'm engaged to Lord Castleroy.

218
00:09:03,070 --> 00:09:04,080
什么...我现在有钱了
Wha-- I'm-I'm a rich man. 

219
00:09:04,090 --> 00:09:07,810
你的确能为我提供舒适的生活
You are a... a comfortable man.

220
00:09:07,930 --> 00:09:09,160
但你的财产
But this w...

221
