他绝不会同意让她们搬去
He'd never agree to let them move to--

229
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:30,900
一个在他看来
what he'd see as some...

230
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:33,740
像死水一样的
...some backwater,

231
