00:09:46,170 --> 00:09:47,530
宏大的海军展示
naval spectacle.

238
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:50,970
看来还是有人会把今天视为庆典
Apparently, there are people who consider today a celebration.

239
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:53,890
我不希望我们就这样分别
I don't want to part like this!

240
00:09:55,790 --> 00:09:59,910
葛瑞尔  某些时候  你需要停止
Greer, at some point, you have to stop piling

241
00:09:59,950 --> 00:10:02,330
把整个家族的问题都堆在自己身上
all of your family's problems on your back.

242
