你需要去冒险
You have to take a risk.

243
00:10:04,450 --> 00:10:07,510
你需要相信爱  相信命运
You have to trust love and fate

244
00:10:08,090 --> 00:10:09,320
相信我
and me.

245
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:27,880
对不起  夫人
Uh, I beg your pardon, ma'am.

246
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:29,100
我在驾驶马车
My carriage is in the road.

247
00:10:29,110 --> 00:10:31,410
送一位贵妇人返回城堡时
I'm taking a noblewoman back to the castle,

248
