如果这位夫人或她的孩子死在这里
What reimbursement will help me

257
00:10:44,230 --> 00:10:45,680
我要补偿又有什么用呢
if this lady dies on my hands?

258
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:48,340
整个法国都将怪罪于我
Or her babe, and all of France will blame me.

259
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:56,680
法国国王  亨利陛下
His Majesty King Henry of France.

260
00:10:57,270 --> 00:11:00,150
苏格兰女王  玛丽陛下
Her Majesty Mary, Queen of Scots.

261
00:11:00,370 --> 00:11:03,550
法国王后  凯瑟琳陛下
Her Majesty Catherine, Queen of France.

262
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:07,210
睁大你们的眼睛  看看法国的力量吧
Turn your eyes on a display of French might.

263
00:11:07,490 --> 00:11:10,720
这场展示是为了向加来之战的英雄们致敬
A spectacle to honor the heroes of Calais.

264
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:15,250
每艘船上
Each ship is full of soldiers

265
00:11:15,250 --> 00:11:16,730
都满载着凯旋的士兵
just returned from our victory.

266
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:17,860
国王万岁
Long live the king!

267
00:11:17,860 --> 00:11:19,990
等着看烟火吧
Wait till you see the fireworks.

268
00:11:19,990 --> 00:11:21,870
愿上帝保佑你  国王陛下
God bless you, Your Majesty!

269
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:24,210
有什么我能为你做的吗  亲爱的
Is there anything I can get you, my dear?

270
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:25,390
要不要来点温暖
Some warm...

271
00:11:25,570 --> 00:11:26,810
香甜的葡萄酒
mulled wine?

272
00:11:27,830 --> 00:11:29,330
不用了  谢谢  我很好
No, thank you. I'm fine.

273
00:11:30,860 --> 00:11:32,300
利思刚刚来找我了
Leith came to see me.

274
00:11:33,340 --> 00:11:35,190
我向他表明我们之间已经结束了
I made it clear to him that we're over,

275
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,310
我会嫁给你  你是我的未来
that I'm marrying you, that you're my future.

276
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:42,640
能不失去我心爱的女人真让我松了一口气
You must allow me to be relieved in not losing the woman I love.

277
00:11:53,780 --> 00:11:54,460
他们竟然让加农炮开火
They're firing cannons.

278
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,150
太奇怪了
How strange.

279
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:57,230
我还以为他们会放烟火
I thought they were using fireworks.

280
00:11:57,260 --> 00:11:58,480
一定是因为
It must be safe enough,

281
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,240
只要他们不互相瞄准  就足够安全
as long as they don't point at each other.

282
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:02,610
加农炮可是很难控制的
Well, cannons can be hard to control.

283
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:04,170
这是胜利的声音
The sound of victory.

284
00:12:04,170 --> 00:12:05,490
是法国的声音
The sound of France.

285
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:08,230
这难道不让你觉得兴奋吗
Doesn't that excite you?

286
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:19,990
天呐  利思就在其中一艘船上
My God, Leith is on one of those ships.

287
00:12:19,990 --> 00:12:21,750
就算是没被炸成碎片的人也活不下来了
Those who aren't blown to bits won't survive.

288
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:24,190
-水太冷了  -我告诉过他们要小心了
- The water's freezing. - I told them to fire with care!

289
00:12:24,190 --> 00:12:26,120
控制开火的人难道是宠物猴吗
Who's manning the guns, a pet monkey?

290
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:28,710
等等  你真的让他们开火了
Wait, you actually told them to fire the cannons?

291
00:12:28,710 --> 00:12:29,560
只有烟火
What kind of spectacle

292
00:12:29,570 --> 00:12:31,730
算得上什么宏大展示呢
would mere fireworks have been, hmm?

293
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:36,020
无所谓了
Well, never mind.

294
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,140
我不许你失望  玛丽
I refuse to have you disappointed, Mary.

295
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,430
这些...
This...

296
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:41,200
都是为你而准备的
is all for you, you know.

297
00:12:42,650 --> 00:12:44,600
-明天还有一次机会  -明天
- There'll be another chance tomorrow. - Tomorrow?

298
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,920
明天我们会再来一次  这回一定要成功
When we'll do it again! Properly this time!

299
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:54,200
上百人就这么死去了
A hundred men dead like that.

300
00:12:54,660 --> 00:12:55,900
生命被如此轻易地夺去
Life so carelessly taken.

301
00:12:55,910 --> 00:12:57,880
感觉好像我是那个失去了理智的人一样
I feel like I'm the one losing my mind.

302
00:12:57,880 --> 00:13:00,350
玛丽  有件事你需要知道
Mary, there's something you should know.

303
00:13:02,070 --> 00:13:04,610
亨利再一次申请废后
Henry asked for an annulment once more.

304
00:13:05,020 --> 00:13:07,120
这只能说明他打算结束我们的婚姻
It can only mean he wishes to end our marriage

305
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:09,110
另娶他人
and turn to someone else.

306
00:13:09,450 --> 00:13:10,590
也就是你
You.

307
00:13:11,130 --> 00:13:11,680
不
No.

308
00:13:11,680 --> 00:13:13,160
我看到了他对你的所作所为
I saw what he did to you.

309
00:13:13,970 --> 00:13:15,260
这简直是莫名其妙
That came out of nowhere.

310
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,200
他从未对我表现出丁点兴趣
He's never shown the slightest bit of interest.

311
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:20,390
一旦他娶了你  他就能够染指英格兰
When he had his hands on you, he had his hands on England.

312
00:13:21,570 --> 00:13:23,370
所以他决定娶我
So he's decided to wed me,

313
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:25,180
让三个国家都归他所有
then keep all three crowns for himself.

314
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:26,890
所以他才突然慷慨地接受了
Thus his suddenly generous acceptance

315
00:13:26,890 --> 00:13:28,810
你没有怀孕这件事
of the fact that you are not pregnant...

316
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:29,790
至今没有怀孕
yet.

317
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:32,060
他想亲自让你怀上子嗣
He wants to give you an heir himself.

318
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:34,180
还有那个如同大屠杀一样的展示  
And the spectacle, the carnage...

319
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:36,970
-拙劣的展示出他的威武  -难道他真认为
- Botched display of his prowess. - Does he honestly think

320
00:13:36,970 --> 00:13:39,360
我和弗朗西斯会同意废除我们的婚姻吗
that Francis and I would agree to have our marriage annulled?

321
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,610
这简直太荒谬了
It's ridiculous!

322
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:47,290
不
No.

323
00:13:47,290 --> 00:13:48,690
他不会这样做的
Even he wouldn't.

324
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:51,200
他要杀害自己的亲生儿子
He's going to kill his own son!

325
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:54,970
如果你所料不错的话
If you're right,

326
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:56,030
我们只有一个机会
our only chance

327
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:57,870
那就是拿下他和他的卫兵
is to overtake him and his guards.

328
00:13:57,870 --> 00:14:00,120
假设弗朗西斯能够说服那些将军
Assuming that Francis is able to persuade the generals

329
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:01,600
