to join us in a coup.

330
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:02,990
如果弗朗西斯回来时
If Francis comes back

331
00:14:02,990 --> 00:14:04,890
走在军队前面  我们就知道他成功了
at the head of an army, we'll know he succeeded.

332
00:14:04,890 --> 00:14:06,250
如果他孤身回来
If he comes back alone,

333
00:14:06,250 --> 00:14:08,020
我们就根本无法反抗亨利
we have no protection from Henry,

334
00:14:08,020 --> 00:14:09,620
弗朗西斯也是如此
and neither does Francis.

335
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:26,220
说你呢
You there,

336
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:26,930
这是怎么回事
what's this?

337
00:14:26,930 --> 00:14:28,100
这是怎么回事
What is this?

338
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,200
发生了什么
What happened here?

339
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:33,310
我请求你们  实话实说
I beg of you, speak freely.

340
00:14:33,650 --> 00:14:36,180
殿下  这就是史上最壮观的海上奇观展示
The greatest naval spectacle of all time, my lord.

341
00:14:36,190 --> 00:14:37,760
直到船爆炸之前
That is, until the ship exploded.

342
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:40,000
国王用火药取代了烟花
The king replaced the fireworks with gunpowder.

343
00:14:40,010 --> 00:14:42,180
他们在加来逃过一劫  到来来确是这样
Can you believe they survived Calais for this?

344
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:43,360
这些士兵都是去过加来的吗
These soldiers are from Calais?

345
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:46,110
明天再次展示时  人数就会翻倍了
There'll be twice as many tomorrow when they do it again.

346
