这不可能
That's impossible.

347
00:14:47,430 --> 00:14:49,750
-谁也不准再进行一次  -请您原谅
- No one would do this again. - Begging your pardon,

348
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:50,480
但你肯定没想到
but you would think no one

349
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:52,380
会有人第一次做出这种事情对吗
would do it the first time, wouldn't you?

350
00:14:52,650 --> 00:14:53,580
但你得想想
Still, you've got to wonder

351
00:14:53,580 --> 00:14:54,700
谁更可怜
who's worse off,

352
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:56,080
是这些可怜人
these poor fellows

